      <title>中国石油进口量再度下降，因最大买家削减进口量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/the-world-s-biggest-oil-buyer-is-cutting-back-on-crude-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，中国的石油进口量再次下降，凸显出这个最大买家的消费疲软，而此时，交易员们还在权衡唐纳德·特朗普入主白宫的影响以及 OPEC+ 可能增加的供应量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/the-world-s-biggest-oil-buyer-is-cutting-back-on-crude-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 05:23:09 GMT</pubDate>
